tr.td:
              Allow one character variable name in

                  initialization expressions in FOR loop if one char variable name
                  is prohibited by {@code format} regexp. For example:



for (int i = 1; i < 10; i++) { // OK
    int j = 1; // violation
}
for (int K = 1; K < 10; K++) { // OK
    int j = 1; // violation
}
List list = new ArrayList();
for (Object o : list) { // OK
    int j = 1; // violation
}
for (Object O : list) { // OK
    int j = 1; // violation
}

